So I am working at constant temperature

243
00:12:24,949 --> 00:12:26,760
in a space where I have

244
00:12:26,760 --> 00:12:29,070
pressure and volume

245
00:12:29,070 --> 00:12:30,730
that can vary.

246
00:12:30,730 --> 00:12:34,079
This is typically what can be done
for example when I work in a confined

247
00:12:34,079 --> 00:12:35,189
space

248
00:12:35,189 --> 00:12:37,720
with a piston which allows us 
to vary

249
00:12:37,720 --> 00:12:40,000
the volume and the pressure.

250
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:45,259
If I am in a volume which is 
relatively large,

251
00:12:45,259 --> 00:12:48,839
I will be at a relatively low 
pressure and the space

252
00:12:48,839 --> 00:12:50,040
will be occupied

253
00:12:50,040 --> 00:12:53,590
by a gas. If I now cross

254
00:12:53,590 --> 00:12:55,720
